A video of a man being robbed in broad daylight in the Joburg CBD has surfaced on social media. In the video, a man wearing brown pants and a pink shirt can be seen being attacked by a group of men in broad day light. As they rob him, the person taking the video can be heard saying: “They are robbing him and people are doing nothing,” After they rob him, the group of men walks down the street as if nothing happened. It is not yet clear when exactly the incident took place. 